    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个塔防重度爱好者，我想做一款反传统的肉鸽塔防，这款《无尽塔防：活下去》是我花了两个月，用『CliCli』做的游戏，有兴趣一起讨论吐槽或者提些建议的话，都欢迎加入我们的Q群：907832371。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>爆爽割草，解压神器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需高频操作，点击即可享受放置肉鸽乐趣；面对无尽的怪潮，装备武器培养塔魂收割怪潮，获取资源升级塔和塔魂，塔+魂双修直面BOSS，享受无尽割草的爆爽快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富多样，耐玩不腻</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近百种独特武器与升级特效，享受割草快感的同时叠加顶级肉鸽体验，让你每次战斗都能收获双倍快感。合理搭配武器和升级效果平衡攻防，才能无限割草无限解压。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>魂塔双修，塔在人在</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索深渊获取魂石，培养塔魂助战。一魂一塔即可分离左右开弓两条弹道，又能合体打造最强防御塔，让你感受割草的极致爽快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>兵来将挡，属性克制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >针对不同敌人，牢记克制口诀：金属克中甲；穿刺克轻甲；魔法克重甲；攻城克强化甲；混乱武器一视同仁，无视护甲！用对了刀割草才能越割越快！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
